  "description": "A parody of <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/developer/sheet/view/developerId,47273/\">Tolkien's</a> Hobbit, <i>An Everyday Tale of a Seeker of Gold</i> is a classic text adventure made using the Quill adventure generation software from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?company=Gilsoft\">Gilsoft</a>. You tell the game what you want to do via a textual interface and the parser is based on verb / noun input.<br><br>Bulbo Biggun the Boggit, at the urging of the wizard Grand Alf goes on a perilous journey. Along with a band of dwarves, he faces ravenous trolls, the treacherous Gullem and Smog the dragon.<br><br>",
